  "text": "As mentioned in the Introduction, most intuitive application of the random unitary channel is the approximate private quantum channel [CITATION_1] , which is a modification of the perfect private quantum channel [CITATION_2] via RUC. The RUCbased APQC is the main tool of constructing the proposed AQSS protocol.",
